'''UVCE''', is an [[acronym]] for '''Unconfined Vapour Cloud Explosion'''.

UVCE's occur with hydrocarbon gases in the air when they find an ignition source the result can be devastating. The combustion pushes all the surrounding unburned gases a high speeds accelerating faster and faster until the gases burns out this heat wave can cause extreme blast damage. A scenario of UVCE might be like a leaky gas valve. Or one you might hear or see of a man leaving his propane stove or device unlit with the gas flowing then dose something dumb like light a cigarette.

